orian" era="ce" normal="1843/1843">1843</unitdate><container id="aspace_d11ed751fb77bfd86c104fd96afe3479" label="Mixed Materials [31924064940921]" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_f67e0f20a35c14f0f6028d85c578832c" parent="aspace_d11ed751fb77bfd86c104fd96afe3479" type="folder">17</container></did></c01><c01 id="aspace_62940ac2599d23a370b4b8062e2b46d4" level="item"><did><unittitle>Tompkins County Election Returns, Nov. 30, 1836-Nov. 22, 1848 . Folder contains returns for various town, county, state, and federal elections held during this period. Articles from <title>Ithaca Daily Chronicle</title> and <title>Ithaca Journal</title>.</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1836-11-30/1848-11-22" type="inclusive">Nov. 30, 1836-Nov. 22, 1848</unitdate><container id="aspace_8205b9988feabf6662a50e5e47f11ad5" label="Mixed Materials [31924064940921]" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_16812785ddbcf71bfe361de74d9b42be" parent="aspace_8205b9988feabf6662a50e5e47f11ad5" type="folder">18</container></did></c01><c01 id="aspace_8a7f96942566fca8837cb11c0479e48f" level="item"><did><unittitle>Articles on slavery, abolition, and colonization, Apr. 5, 1837-Apr. 18, 1838. Folder contains assorted articles on the issues surrounding slavery. Articles from <title>Ithaca Daily Chronicle</title> and <title>The Ithaca Journal and Herald</title>.</unittitle><container id="aspace_1c886e777decfbe44a629cedc2f13b1e" label="Mixed Materials [31924064940921]" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_63118f7fc465b9fe28ab25bbf86ecee2" parent="aspace_1c886e777decfbe44a629cedc2f13b1e" type="folder">19</container></did></c01><c01 id="aspace_1c38f12fd9778ac3db661a741f138526" level="item"><did><unittitle>Residents of Tompkins County call meeting to discuss fiscal problems they believe caused by politicians in Albany. Article appears in May 7, 1834 <title>Ithaca Daily Chronicle</title>.</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1834-05-07/1834-05-